choices.text: You are given a sequence of real numbers. You have to perform n operations on these numbers. Each operation goes as follows: choose indexes i and j (i   j) that haven't been chosen yet; round element a_{i} to the nearest integer that isn't more than a_{i} (assign to a_{i}:   a_{i}  ); round element a_{j} to the nearest integer that isn't less than a_{j} (assign to a_{j}:   a_{j}  ).
